OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry, bright morning,
OL,6,Fperhaps the odd light shower. Turning
OL,7,Fovercast through the afternoon as rain
OL,8,Fspreads in from the west later,
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy, damp evening with
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain. Turning drier
OL,13,Fthrough the rest of the night with
OL,14,Fsome clearer spells developing.
OL,15,FBlustery winds, strong at times.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,18,Fdry day, with plenty of sunny spells
OL,19,Fand just the slight chance of an
OL,20,Fisolated light shower in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
